<section class="container-fluid">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 blurb">
       <p class="blurb_text">fullfill is a self-improvement website for learning about and adapting new life changes. We are here to help you create and maintain good habits.</p>
       <p class="blurb_text">Get started below<p>
</div>
</div>
